# Orrery ‚Äî Cursor rule

**Keep in sync with `CLAUDE.md` at the repo root.** When you change project rules, update both files so Claude Code, Cursor, and humans see the same contract.

Instructions for agentic AI working on this codebase. Read this before touching any file.

